# Feature Flags

Goal: Prevent path/layout disagreements between agents.

- Feature flags required for risky rollouts / schema migrations / pricing changes
- Provider interface:
  - env flags locally
  - Vercel Feature Flags in prod
- Hook: `useFeatureFlag("flag")`
- Server guard: `requireFlag("flag")`
- Feature flag utility: `src/lib/feature-flags.ts`
- Default value for missing flags: `false`
- Type-safe flag names (no magic strings)
